# app-url

## iCloud 各应用网址（默认英文版）

- <https://www.icloud.com/mail>
- <https://www.icloud.com/contacts>
- <https://www.icloud.com/calendar>
- <https://www.icloud.com/photos>
- <https://www.icloud.com/iclouddrive>
- <https://www.icloud.com/notes>
- <https://www.icloud.com/reminders>
- <https://www.icloud.com/invites>
- <https://www.icloud.com/pages>
- <https://www.icloud.com/numbers>
- <https://www.icloud.com/keynote>
- <https://www.icloud.com/find>
- <https://www.icloud.com/setting>

## iCloud 多语言网址格式规范

默认英文版本 mail 为例：

- 英文 en <https://www.icloud.com/mail>

其他语言版本规则为：

- 法语 fr <https://www.icloud.com/fr-fr/mail>
- 葡萄牙语（巴西） pt_BR <https://www.icloud.com/pt-br/mail>
- 日语 ja <https://www.icloud.com/ja-jp/mail>
- 印地语 hi <https://www.icloud.com/hi-in/mail>
- 德语 de <https://www.icloud.com/de-de/mail>
- 韩语 ko <https://www.icloud.com/ko-kr/mail>
- 意大利语 it <https://www.icloud.com/it-it/mail>
- 泰语 th <https://www.icloud.com/th-th/mail>
- 西班牙语 es <https://www.icloud.com/es-es/mail>
- 荷兰语 nl <https://www.icloud.com/nl-nl/mail>
- 中文（台湾） zh_TW <https://www.icloud.com/zh-tw/mail>
- 波兰语 pl <https://www.icloud.com/pl-pl/mail>
- 俄语 ru <https://www.icloud.com/ru-ru/mail>
- 土耳其语 tr <https://www.icloud.com/tr-tr/mail>
- 希伯来语 he <https://www.icloud.com/iw-il/mail>
- 阿拉伯语 ar <https://www.icloud.com/ar-sa/mail>
- 马来语 ms <https://www.icloud.com/ms-my/mail>
- 葡萄牙语（葡萄牙） pt_PT <https://www.icloud.com/pt-pt/mail>
- 瑞典语 sv <https://www.icloud.com/sv-se/mail>
- 丹麦语 da <https://www.icloud.com/da-dk/mail>
- 越南语 vi <https://www.icloud.com/vi-vi/mail>
- 印度尼西亚语 id <https://www.icloud.com/id-id/mail>
- 中文（中国） zh_CN <https://www.icloud.com.cn/mail>
- 捷克语 cs <https://www.icloud.com/cs-cz/mail>
- 挪威语 no <https://www.icloud.com/no-no/mail>
- 匈牙利语 hu <https://www.icloud.com/hu-hu/mail>
- 希腊语 el <https://www.icloud.com/el-gr/mail>
- 乌克兰语 uk <https://www.icloud.com/uk-ua/mail>
- 罗马尼亚语 ro <https://www.icloud.com/ro-ro/mail>
- 芬兰语 fi <https://www.icloud.com/fi-fi/mail>
- 克罗地亚语 hr <https://www.icloud.com/hr-hr/mail>
- 斯洛文尼亚语 sl <https://www.icloud.com/sl-si/mail>
- 斯洛伐克语 sk <https://www.icloud.com/sk-sk/mail>
